# the plain (no-interpolation-inside-the-inner-literal) case. The outer f`
# lowers to a string concat where the hole's value is the inner literal's own
# lowering; both are pure string concatenation, so this pins the simplest
# body-position nesting shape (no filter, no error, no ctx).
